  "tune": "Kremser",
  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "We gather together to ask the Lord&#39;s blessing; He chastens and hastens His will to make known. The wicked oppressing now cease from distressing. Sing praises to His Name; He forgets not His own.",
    "v2": "Beside us to guide us, our God with us joining, Ordaining, maintaining His kingdom divine; So from the beginning the fight we were winning; Thou, Lord, were at our side, all glory be Thine!",
    "v3": "We all do extol Thee, Thou Leader triumphant, And pray that Thou still our Defender will be. Let Thy congregation escape tribu- lation; Thy Name be ever praised! O Lord, make us free!"
  },
